name: ripgrep
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "13.0.0" %}

package:
  name: ripgrep
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/BurntSushi/ripgrep/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 0fb17aaf285b3eee8ddab17b833af1e190d73de317ff9648751ab0660d763ed2

build:
  number: 2

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('rust') }}
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - cargo-bundle-licenses
    - asciidoctor                      # [not win]

test:
  commands:
    - rg --help

about:
  home: https://github.com/BurntSushi/ripgrep
  license: MIT
  summary: ripgrep recursively searches directories for a regex pattern
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: 
    - LICENSE-MIT
    - THIRDPARTY.yml

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - dbast
    - seanyen
